Message:
 Got it, Alicia! If you want to track multiple purchase amounts, you would typically send separate events for each purchase. Each event would have its own `nb_value`. Here's an example of how you might do this in your pixel code:
```javascript
// First purchase event
{nb_value: 49.99}
// Second purchase event
{nb_value: 29.99}
```
Each of these events will be tracked separately with their respective values.
If you need further assistance or have more questions, feel free to ask!
